{"tid":2345383,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"日本IG女神上電視示範炒飯　圖人不符真身似路人甲　全民炒車怒轟詐騙","createTime":"2020-12-29T12:27:17.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-02T04:45:25.000Z","uid":147522,"like":13,"dislike":328,"uniUserReply":90,"replies":[{"pid":"a4f2efe5a57951d54acd5b0bb386564d9cc54950","tid":2345383,"uid":147522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-29T12:27:17.000Z","msg":"網絡世界常有「照騙」，但一時騙得過網民，始終都要用真面目示人。日本有一位IG女神，最近受邀上電視節目，結果網民發現電視上的她，與平日在IG上的她，簡直判若兩人！<br />\n<br />\n女神名叫Makimiku，今年23歲，由神奈川縣去到東京工作，現在是自由身模特兒。上月她受邀上電視節目《噂の！東京マガジン》挑戰煮中式炒飯，結果她真人一露面，未炒飯已「炒晒車」，與IG平時的圖片相差甚遠。網民留言指，果然不應該相信IG和抖音，這兩個應用程式簡直是「照騙天堂」。<br />\n<br />\n有人指修圖修這麼誇張比整容還差，因為整容的人起碼真人是好看的。不過亦有人覺得她真人看起來比IG的假照自然得多，反而顯得有點可愛，又有人表示喜歡她真人的樣子，真是各花入各眼。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CP7j5YE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCP7j5YE.jpg&h=8270326c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iOEFQqk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiOEFQqk.jpg&h=477a156e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KUeRW5k.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKUeRW5k.jpg&h=6d56271a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fuAeaqm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfuAeaqm.jpg&h=9e2c7387&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MGLtZiH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMGLtZiH.jpg&h=bc1f87a7&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/P44yqYH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FP44yqYH.jpg&h=1a375922&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0qrMLYJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0qrMLYJ.jpg&h=ae8dd0c8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3e9edccd62291238b07810ec86121a2286c624cf","tid":2345383,"uid":155818,"like":7,"dislike":2,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-29T12:28:08.000Z","msg":"好能圓"},{"pid":"8465